{"id":1227,"date":"2025-04-12T00:05:19","date_gmt":"2025-04-11T17:05:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1227"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:38:33","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:38:33","slug":"nam-trung-bi","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/nam-trung-bi\/","title":{"rendered":"N\u00e1m trung b\u00ec"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p t\u00e1i sinh l\u00e0n da n\u00e1m, s\u1ea1m, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 melanin m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn l\u1ecdc, t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o melanin, ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da xung quanh.<\/li>\n<li>K\u00edch th\u00edch t\u0103ng sinh collagen, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da.<\/li>\n<li>Ra s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u sau m\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>V\u1edbi \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Mesotherapy s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea7u kim ti\u00eam vi \u0111i\u1ec3m, \u0111\u01b0a ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o trung b\u00ec c\u1ee7a da. C\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 melanin, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ee9t g\u00e3y li\u00ean k\u1ebft n\u00e1m v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c n\u00e1m v\u1edbi Tranexamic Acid 3%, 4-n-Butylresorcinol 1%, Alpha Arbutin 0.5%, Niacinamide 5% ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba, l\u00e0m m\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1m n\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0u da, duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng, m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn.<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ed9 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi 3 in 1: Duy tr\u00ec &#8211; Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i &#8211; B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 1 &#8211; 2 ti\u1ebfng<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 03 \u2013 05 l\u1ea7n, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1ea7n kho\u1ea3ng 30 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -6px; top: 416.556px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p t\u00e1i sinh l\u00e0n da n\u00e1m, s\u1ea1m, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3631,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[39],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1227","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-sac-to","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1227","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1227"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3631"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1227"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=1227"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=1227"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"hr